## My process

### Built with

- Semantic HTML5 markup
- CSS custom properties
- Flexbox
- Mobile-first workflow

### What I learned

In this project, I learnt to use the mobile-first work flow and practised the Semantic HTML5 markup and also learnd how to use the CSS well enough.

### Continued development

Need to keep improving my Semantic HTML5 and CSS skills, and how to make wabpage more responsive and accessible. 
